(688, 78, 'first_section_text', 'To design a B2B presentation box that could safely contain and transport three multi-tool products within their original packaging. It also had to contain a USB stick and A4 brochure. \r\n\r\nThe boxes were to be mailed to new potential stockists.\r\n'),
