(726, 90, 'first_section_text', 'To provide a new mailing format to replace (and hopefully out-perform!) the current control pack. The new format had to provide more selling space but remain within budget. It also had to comply with strict insert specifications.'),
(727, 90, '_first_section_text', 'field_547f453fdf3ef'),
(728, 90, 'second_section_heading', 'OUR IDEA'),
(729, 90, '_second_section_heading', 'field_547f466058a3b'),
(730, 90, 'second_section_text', 'To create an eye-catching and engaging format that would grab reader attention, encourage them to read more and request further information. Our idea featured a ''stepped edge index to help identify the important information and an easy to use reply mechanism was designed to meet royal mail response specification.'),
(731, 90, '_second_section_text', 'field_547f46ba58a3c'),
