(739, 90, '_third_section_sub_heading', 'field_547f4c0f10594'),
(740, 90, 'third_section_text', 'The results from our new format were so impressive (64% increase in response over a six month period) against the control pack that Holiday Property Bond subsequently adopted our format to roll out across their direct mail activity as well. Whats more, in the process we also managed to lower print costs by 7%. '),
