(322, 1, '2015-07-04 16:33:59', '2015-07-04 16:33:59', 'W&amp;L provide a printing service to Capital One and have been a supplier for over 3 years. They are also responsible for the delivery of all printed items to various insertion houses. Deliveries are always timely and to the schedule provided.The quality of our inserts is paramount to their success. There have been no issues with the quality of the printed piece in the entire time of working with Waddington &amp; Ledger. They set the standards on quality customer service. They perform on a level not seen from other suppliers of this type.', 'Helen Diamand, Marketing Services Manager, Capital One', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '322', '', '', '2015-07-10 17:01:51', '2015-07-10 17:01:51', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~wlprintco/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=322', 0, 'testimonial', '', 0),
(323, 1, '2015-07-06 07:15:35', '2015-07-06 07:15:35', 'The app form you did for the Boots Health Club in April was a great success (hurrah) and looks great bound into the Health and Beauty magazine, so thanks for that - and the extra perf!', 'Nicky Milne, Production Controller, Boots Health and Beauty Magazine', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'helen-diamand-marketing-services-manager', '', '', '2015-07-10 17:00:31', '2015-07-10 17:00:31', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~wlprintco/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=323', 0, 'testimonial', '', 0),
(324, 1, '2015-07-06 08:05:17', '2015-07-06 08:05:17', 'I just wanted to pass on my thanks to you guys for your assistance with our colour problem and the loan of Michael for the day!I have to say we were all suitably impressed by his amazing knowledge of all things print and colour.Our customer was blown away and very happy with the input. It has really helped us.Thank you very much.', 'Andy Lovelock, Account Manager, Canon Business Services', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'helen-diamand-marketing-services-manager-2', '', '', '2015-07-10 17:03:58', '2015-07-10 17:03:58', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~wlprintco/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=324', 0, 'testimonial', '', 0),
(325, 1, '2015-07-06 08:05:30', '2015-07-06 08:05:30', 'Just wanted to let you know that the materials you produced for this job were greatly appreciated and the client was very pleased with the overall quality. The photo reproduction was excellent and the booth display proved to be very striking and popular at the climate conference in Peru.', 'Graham Winter, Christian Aid', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'helen-diamand-marketing-services-manager-3', '', '', '2015-07-10 17:06:15', '2015-07-10 17:06:15', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~wlprintco/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=325', 0, 'testimonial', '', 0),
(326, 1, '2015-07-06 08:05:44', '2015-07-06 08:05:44', 'Just seen the wraparound stand and wanted to say thank you for such a great job and turning it around so quickly.', 'Kim Golding, John Lewis ', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'helen-diamand-marketing-services-manager-4', '', '', '2015-07-10 17:04:38', '2015-07-10 17:04:38', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~wlprintco/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=326', 0, 'testimonial', '', 0),
(327, 1, '2015-07-06 09:39:50', '2015-07-06 09:39:50', 'You''ve done a great job. I''m very pleased both with the quality of the production and also your efficient service. I look forward to working with you again soon.', 'Alex Klee, Lloyds TSB', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'helen-diamand-marketing-services-manager-5', '', '', '2015-07-10 17:07:07', '2015-07-10 17:07:07', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~wlprintco/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=327', 0, 'testimonial', '', 0),
