(3, 3, 'casestudies_category', 'To remain successful and continually increase market share businesses need a clear idea of what they stand for. From here we develop effective brand strategies that ensure a business retains its competitive edge and long-term profitability. <strong>Out-thinking the competition</strong> is our prime motivation. For those clients without a clear understanding of what they stand for we can and do help them discover their sustainable competitive advantage.', 0, 3),
(4, 4, 'casestudies_category', 'We believe <strong>ideas count</strong> and that visual and verbal story telling is the most effective way to engage customers and sell more products and services. Our creative work is intended to win sales for our clients not awards for us. The idea always comes first, not the choice of media. We enjoy making all of our clients <strong>look better than the competition</strong>.', 0, 6),
(5, 5, 'casestudies_category', 'Great ideas and stunning creative are worthless until they are brought to life. Our team of production experts can work across all media. They have an eye for detail and a reputation for solving problems. Over the years our production ideas have helped leading brands sell their products more effectively.  ', 0, 6),
(6, 6, 'casestudies_category', 'We think it essential to have a clear understanding of our clients business objectives and issues before we begin the creative process. Only after we have these can we start to develop a creative idea that will satisfy these objectives and issues.', 0, 3),
(7, 7, 'casestudies_category', 'We live in a digital world that now connects us to almost everything we want to do. We help businesses improve their digital presence in all its forms. As results matter to us we constantly monitor our clients digital activity to ensure response levels are high across all platforms.', 0, 2),
